snippet.title: Shonduras
snippet.description:
join our family for some BEST DAYS EVER!!
this vlog is part of our family since years and years ago, you share our memories, and feel like part of the crew!

MEET THE FAMILY:
Dad, has a Spacestation and is always busy and always having fun!
Mom,  is a Supermom that keeps our house together and somewhat normal!
Adley, is a ball of energy that keeps everyone in our family smiling always!
Niko Bear, is part dinosaur, part shark, part pirate, part the best brother ever!
Navey, our newest cutest toughest little sister :)
